trans-unit.source: Provides the system implementation for displaying a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller systemimplementering för att visa en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The ContextMenuService class provides attached properties that can be used to specify the appearance and position of a context menu.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ContextMenuService ger bifogade egenskaper som kan användas för att ange hur och var en snabbmeny.

trans-unit.source: Many of the properties in the ContextMenuService class are also defined by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>.
trans-unit.target: Många av egenskaperna i klassen ContextMenuService också definieras av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>

trans-unit.source: Sometimes it is more convenient to set the properties by using the ContextMenuService class than by setting the properties on a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>.
trans-unit.target: Ibland är det mer praktiskt att ange egenskaper med klassen ContextMenuService än genom att ange egenskaperna för en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can create a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu> to be shared by multiple elements, but use the ContextMenuService class to specify a different position of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu> for each element.
trans-unit.target: Du kan till exempel skapa en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>för att delas av flera element, men använder klassen ContextMenuService för att ange en annan plats för den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>för varje element.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>

trans-unit.source: The following properties are defined by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu> and ContextMenuService classes.
trans-unit.target: Följande egenskaper har definierats av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>och ContextMenuService klasser.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>

trans-unit.source: If any of these properties are set on both <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu> and the ContextMenuService, the property value from the ContextMenuService is used.
trans-unit.target: Om någon av dessa egenskaper anges på båda <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>och ContextMenuService, egenskapsvärdet hämtas från ContextMenuService används.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenu>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.Placement%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.PlacementRectangle%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.PlacementTargetProperty> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.HorizontalOffset%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.VerticalOffsetProperty> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.HasDropShadow%2A> You can also use the ContextMenuService to display menus on disabled items.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.Placement%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.PlacementRectangle%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.PlacementTargetProperty>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.HorizontalOffset%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.VerticalOffsetProperty>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.HasDropShadow%2A>Du kan också använda ContextMenuService för att visa menyer på inaktiverade objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.HasDropShadow%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.VerticalOffsetProperty> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.HorizontalOffset%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.PlacementTargetProperty> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.PlacementRectangle%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContextMenuService.Placement%2A>
